                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.6363 Manchuria/255: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-10-28T13:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 28, 1935—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>42. Tokyo’s 196, October 22, 5 p.m. Department in no way dissents from views
                    expressed by Neville and expressly concurs in view contained in his last
                    sentence.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
